### calcular costo envío estándar
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shipping/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "STANDARD",
  "weight": 5.0,
  "distance": 10.0
}

### calcular costo envío express
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shipping/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "EXPRESS",
  "weight": 5.0,
  "distance": 10.0
}

### calcular costo envío internacional
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/shipping/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
